casebody.data:
Submitted on record and briefs December 19, 1991, STATE OF OREGON, Respondent, v. RAYMOND JOHN MARTSCH, Appellant. (90CR2527; CA A68397) 822 P2d 759 James C. Coffey and Stebbins & Coffey, North Bend, filed the brief for appellant. Dave Frohnmayer, Attorney General, Virginia L. Linder, Solicitor General, and Timothy A. Sylwester, Assistant Attorney General, Salem, filed the brief for respondent. PER CURIAM

reversed and remanded with instructions to dismiss indictment January 22,

reconsideration denied April 15,

petition for review allowed August 25, 1992 (314 Or 175)

Before Richardson, Presiding Judge, and Deits and Durham, Judges.
